# Setup: https://www.callmebot.com/blog/free-api-whatsapp-messages/
#
# Each staff member needs to:
# 1. Save +34 623 78 95 80 as "CallMeBot" in contacts
# 2. Send "I allow callmebot to send me messages" via WhatsApp
# 3. Receive API key in response
#
# Format: phone:apikey (comma-separated for multiple recipients)
# Example: +46701234567:123456,+46709876543:789012
